{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x17df2d",
      "back_en": "They could distrust us now, as a result of that.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Meaning preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17df5e",
      "back_en": "Damn. If it's true, this could get pretty bad...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e282",
      "back_en": "Who's this?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e296",
      "back_en": "You mean...?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'You don't mean...?' carries disbelief; 'Você quer dizer...?' is neutral. Prefer 'Não me diga que...?'"
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e2a9",
      "back_en": "Correct... The Mikado himself.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e2c8",
      "back_en": "The Mikado... the god incarnate who rules",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e32e",
      "back_en": "Just a common people really...?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'commoner' = plebeu; 'povo comum' is collective and ungrammatical here. Use 'plebeu comum'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e524",
      "back_en": "stressful!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e5c3",
      "back_en": "country!? That'll be nothing but trouble!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e6f0",
      "back_en": "the emperor or something?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17e9af",
      "back_en": "I would be forced to cut you down on the spot",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ea13",
      "back_en": "H-Hey! Y-You can't just say that so shamelessly!",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'nonchalantly' = despreocupadamente/casualmente, not 'desavergonhadamente' (shamelessly)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ec31",
      "back_en": "do someth--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ec7a",
      "back_en": "...Where the hell did she go!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ed0b",
      "back_en": "soldiers drag me out of the room.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ed2e",
      "back_en": "Our esteemed guest from afar, Sir Haku, has arrived!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'estimado' added but acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17edc1",
      "back_en": "I look like a clown...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ee07",
      "back_en": "path are full of guys looking pompous.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Awkward 'com cara de pomposos' but meaning ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17ee60",
      "back_en": "at my side, murmurs quietly to me.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f19b",
      "back_en": "I trust all is well.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f20c",
      "back_en": "...So the man at your side would be Haku?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f2a3",
      "back_en": "You may raise your head.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f322",
      "back_en": "there, his face hidden. The Mikado, I presume.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f41f",
      "back_en": "next to him.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f42c",
      "back_en": "...What--!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f437",
      "back_en": "H-Honoka...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f444",
      "back_en": "The woman standing there is, without a doubt,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f474",
      "back_en": "Honoka.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f47c",
      "back_en": "What... What's she doing here...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f4a0",
      "back_en": "Why is she standing next to the Mikado...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f5c4",
      "back_en": "It's not the time to say I think I know",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f5f4",
      "back_en": "the woman beside him. I'd sound like I",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f61f",
      "back_en": "flirting with her.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f62f",
      "back_en": "I-I just... I have a strange feeling we've",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f662",
      "back_en": "from somewhere before.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f7d2",
      "back_en": "Mikado's words, but my questions remain...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f7fd",
      "back_en": "What does this mean? Could it be the same person?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f82c",
      "back_en": "Maybe they look alike? Could they be sisters?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'pareçam semelhantes' fine for look alike."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17f935",
      "back_en": "I do not deserve such praise, sir...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17fcfc",
      "back_en": "Huh--!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17fd04",
      "back_en": "They're... girls?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18006f",
      "back_en": "This shall be your reward.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1801d4",
      "back_en": "To mark our oath.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180208",
      "back_en": "and offer to you everything that we are.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180231",
      "back_en": "Eternal loyalty to our Master.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18025c",
      "back_en": "From this moment on, these two are yours--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18028d",
      "back_en": "body, mind, and soul.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1802a3",
      "back_en": "Command them as you see fit. You may treat them",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1802d5",
      "back_en": "with care, or use them to satisfy your",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'toy with them' = brincar com elas; 'usá-las' loses the playful/toying nuance."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180303",
      "back_en": "your own desires. Nothing will be denied to you.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Você não será negado nada' is ungrammatical; use 'Nada lhe será negado'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18032c",
      "back_en": "H-Hold on. This is a little--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18034a",
      "back_en": "I thank you, Haku, for the time well spent.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'bem gasto' ok; 'bem aproveitado' more natural."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180448",
      "back_en": "As Honoka leaves, she quickly turns to me.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180473",
      "back_en": "Please take good care of my daughters.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1804b5",
      "back_en": "Your daughters!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18053d",
      "back_en": "I rise, calling to them without thinking.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1805b8",
      "back_en": "It is time to depart.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1805ce",
      "back_en": "Huh? But... what about...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1806bb",
      "back_en": "He may have rescued Her Highness, but even so...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180749",
      "back_en": "gift...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180784",
      "back_en": "thinking!? This is unforgivable!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1807a5",
      "back_en": "Silence!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1807ae",
      "back_en": "Nyergh...!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1807ec",
      "back_en": "ever need the forgiveness of a nobody like you?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'offal' rendered as 'nulidade'; acceptable insult."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180849",
      "back_en": "insolent fool!? You will learn your place!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180873",
      "back_en": "Nyeh... H-H-How dare you challenge me--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1808cc",
      "back_en": "thinking you're special in some way?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180926",
      "back_en": "Nyarrrrgh...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180a28",
      "back_en": "You seem destined to have a really strange life.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180af8",
      "back_en": "the Kamunagi of Chains.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180baa",
      "back_en": "of Lady High Priestess Honoka -- her successors.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180e81",
      "back_en": "received as great an honor as that one moments ago.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180ee0",
      "back_en": "Mikado. Words do not do the honor justice.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180f69",
      "back_en": "for better or for worse.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'para bem ou para mal' slightly clipped idiom; ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x180fba",
      "back_en": "I said you are destined for a strange life.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1810ba",
      "back_en": "What the hell do I do with these two?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1811ea",
      "back_en": "was a shock, but she has daughters this old?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'filhas tão velhas' (so old) is odd; 'this old' suits 'filhas já dessa idade/tão crescidas'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1812d9",
      "back_en": "Oh, Kuon. Well, the reward was, uh...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1813c4",
      "back_en": "And, ah... Who are they?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18140d",
      "back_en": "and dressed in rather revealing fashion.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x181496",
      "back_en": "The Mikado kinda said I can have them.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1814e0",
      "back_en": "These two... are the reward?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1814fd",
      "back_en": "We now belong to our Master.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18151a",
      "back_en": "We just recently became our Master's body-and-soul servants,",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Adds 'servas de corpo e alma' not present; source line ends at 'Master's'. Possible over-translation/line merge."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18156b",
      "back_en": "A pleasure to meet you.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x181583",
      "back_en": "Bfff!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Onomatopoeia acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1815d9",
      "back_en": "We shall take care of all your needs.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18166d",
      "back_en": "his &&.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Placeholder preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x181675",
      "back_en": "For that is the sole purpose of our existence.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1816b7",
      "back_en": "What the hell are these girls saying!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x181720",
      "back_en": "worm--no, even lower...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'maggot' as 'verme' close enough."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x181766",
      "back_en": "yourself a little harem here. Marvelous work.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1817ed",
      "back_en": "Mikado!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correct."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1818af",
      "back_en": "of person... I believe in you...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1818fc",
      "back_en": "stings the most...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 95
}